<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6b910509-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s1108"><num value="1108">§ 1108.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out this subchapter, but sums appropriated for any one fiscal year shall not exceed $1,200,000.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6b91050a-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/pl/89/454/tI/s9">Pub. L. 89–454, title I, § 9</ref>, <date date="1966-06-17">June 17, 1966</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/80/208">80 Stat. 208</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/89/688/s2/b">Pub. L. 89–688, § 2(b)</ref>, <date date="1966-10-15">Oct. 15, 1966</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/80/1001">80 Stat. 1001</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/91/15/s2">Pub. L. 91–15, § 2</ref>, <date date="1969-05-23">May 23, 1969</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/83/10">83 Stat. 10</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id6b91050b-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id6b91050c-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id6b91050d-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1969—<ref href="/us/pl/91/15">Pub. L. 91–15</ref> substituted “$1,200,000” for “$1,500,000”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1966—<ref href="/us/pl/89/688">Pub. L. 89–688</ref> substituted “this title” for “this Act”, which, for purposes of codification, has been changed to “this subchapter”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
